As an Admin, I want to:

Log in to the admin portal
Add, update, and remove doctors
Manage system users (patients and doctors)
Monitor appointments across the system
Acceptance Criteria:

Admin can manage doctor profiles
Admin can view system-wide data
Admin has restricted secure access

As a Patient, I want to:

Register and log in to the system
Search for doctors by name or specialty
Book appointments
View my upcoming appointments
View prescriptions given by doctors
Acceptance Criteria:

Patient can securely log in
Patient can search for doctors
Patient can book and view appointments

As a Doctor, I want to:

Log in to the system securely
View my scheduled appointments
Manage patient consultations
Update prescription details
View patient medical history
Acceptance Criteria:

Doctor can authenticate using login credentials
Doctor can view only their assigned appointments
Doctor can update the appointment status
